Hints for setup:

1. These folders need to be installed:

 - mkdir anhang
 - mkdir ir
 - mkdir mailer_dir

 All of these folders need CHMOD 777
 
2. In order to see graphs you need the GD lib

3. As CRONJOB you need

00 02 * * * cd /your_path; php ./script_serienaufgabe.php > /dev/null 2>&1

In case of questions send a mail to: marcus@taskito.de
